    "title": {
      "rendered": "Five Ways to Build Your Nonprofit\u2019s Mobile Subscriber List"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Mobile-Websites-and-Technol.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-13156\" alt=\"Mobile-Websites-and-Technol\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Mobile-Websites-and-Technol-300x300.png?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Mobile-Websites-and-Technol.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Mobile-Websites-and-Technol.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Mobile-Websites-and-Technol.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Mobile-Websites-and-Technol.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Mobile-Websites-and-Technol.png?w=510&amp;ssl=1 510w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>A well-promoted mobile alert campaign is hard to find in the nonprofit sector. If a nonprofit is going to invest in mobile alerts, then mobile opt-ins and short code and keyword pitches should be integrated into multiple communication channels such as print, web, email, and social and mobile media. Yet strangely, it rarely happens. Mobile alerts and text-to-give campaigns seem to be managed, implemented, and promoted completely in isolation from an organization&#8217;s primary communications and fundraising strategies. The disconnect is profound and has been for years.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The good news is that some nonprofits are getting more creative and strategic about building their mobile lists and leading the way in discovering new best practices for building mobile subscriber lists.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>1. Add a mobile opt-in to your e-newsletter.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.unicefusa.org/hidden/sign-up-for-mobile-updates.html?utm_source=enews_050213&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=usf\">Subscribe UNICEF USA </a></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/unicef-mobile-list-1.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12612\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"UNICEF Mobile List 1\" src=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/unicef-mobile-list-1.png?resize=600%2C272\" width=\"600\" height=\"272\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/unicef-mobile-list-2.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12613\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"UNICEF Mobile List 2\" src=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/unicef-mobile-list-2.png?resize=600%2C351\" width=\"600\" height=\"351\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n2. Add a mobile opt-in to your website and blog.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.salarmychicago.org/mobile/index.htm\">Subscribe Salvation Army</a></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/salvation-army.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12615\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Salvation Army\" src=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/salvation-army.png?resize=600%2C251\" width=\"600\" height=\"251\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/salvation-army-blog1.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12617\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Salvation Army Blog\" src=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/salvation-army-blog1.png?resize=600%2C359\" width=\"600\" height=\"359\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n3. Add a mobile opt-in to your e-newsletter opt-in.<a href=\"http://www.peta.org/\"><br />\n</a><a href=\"http://www.peta.org/about/learn-about-peta/subscribe-to-mobile-alerts.aspx\">Subscribe Peta</a></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/peta.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12620\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Peta\" src=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/peta.png?resize=600%2C315\" width=\"600\" height=\"315\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n4. Add a mobile opt-in to your mobile website.<br />\n<a href=\"http://action.humanesociety.org/site/PageServer?pagename=textsignup\">Subscribe Humane Society of the United States</a></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/hsus-mobile-alerts.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12628\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"HSUS-Mobile-Alerts\" src=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/hsus-mobile-alerts.png?resize=512%2C768\" width=\"512\" height=\"768\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n5. Promote your short code and keyword pitch on social media.<br />\n<a href=\"https://text4baby.org/index.php/sign-up\">Subscribe Text4Baby.org</a></strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> <a href=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/text4baby-mobile-alerts.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12626\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"text4baby-mobile-alerts\" src=\"http://nonprofitorgs.files.wordpress.com/2013/06/text4baby-mobile-alerts.png?resize=512%2C330\" width=\"512\" height=\"330\" /></a></strong></p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
